KitKat::

She smiled at him. "I understand. After all, we are at war. It would 
not look good to have me walking freely at your side around your 
base. No, I would not ask that you dishonor yourself in that fashion."
She looked down and sighed forlornly. "Perhaps I should just go?" in 
a soft and sad voice.
